description.fr: {God:5} a disparu dans les galeries lors d'un assaut de Shushus. {CharacterName:474} accompagne {CharacterName:873} à {Nation:156} pour retrouver le dieu.
description.en: {God:5} disappeared in the tunnels during a Shushu attack. {CharacterName:474} and {CharacterName:873} are headed to {Nation:156} to find the god.
description.es: {God:5} ha desaparecido en las galerías durante un asalto de fab'huritus. {CharacterName:474} acompaña a {CharacterName:873} a {Nation:156} para ir a ver al dios.
description.de: {God:5} ist während eines Shushu-Angriffs in den Tunneln verschwunden. {CharacterName:474} begleitet {CharacterName:873} nach {Nation:156}, um den Gott wiederzufinden.
description.pt: {God:5} desapareceu nas galerias durante um ataque de Shushus. {CharacterName:474} acompanha {CharacterName:873} a {Nation:156} para encontrar o deus.

descriptionFinished.fr: Pour être plus efficaces dans leur recherche, {CharacterName:873} et {CharacterName:474} prennent deux chemins différents. {CharacterName:873} trouve {God:5}, mais… à la surprise générale, {CharacterName:474} aussi. Reste à déterminer lequel est le vrai dieu.
descriptionFinished.en: To search more efficiently, {CharacterName:873} and {CharacterName:474} took two different paths. {CharacterName:873} found {God:5} but… to everyone's surprise, so did {CharacterName:474}. Now, they need to figure out which is the real god.
descriptionFinished.es: Para ser más eficaces en su búsqueda, {CharacterName:873} y {CharacterName:474} toman dos caminos diferentes. {CharacterName:873} encuentra a {God:5}, pero… para sorpresa de todos, {CharacterName:474} también. Queda por determinar cuál de los dos es el verdadero dios.
descriptionFinished.de: Um ihre Suche effektiver zu gestalten, schlagen {CharacterName:873} und {CharacterName:474} unterschiedliche Wege ein. {CharacterName:873} findet {God:5}, aber zur Überraschung aller\_… {CharacterName:474} ebenfalls. Jetzt muss nur noch geklärt werden, wer der richtige Gott ist.
descriptionFinished.pt: Para serem mais eficazes em sua busca, {CharacterName:873} e {CharacterName:474} seguem dois caminhos diferentes. {CharacterName:873} encontra {God:5}, mas… para surpresa geral, {CharacterName:474} também. Agora, resta determinar qual é o verdadeiro deus.
